三、教學目標 Objectives


１、社會人?基本?學?２、社會人?�鷋�?學?３、日本?習慣?慣??４、日本文化?慣??５、仕事?話?方?慣??６、日本?留學?????目標???７、日本???????????行????目標???８、日本企業?就職?????目標???９、日本?働????目標??? 


The objectives of this course include the following: 1. to learn the basics of a businessperson2. to learn business etiquette3. to get accustomed to common business practices in Japan4. to get accustomed to Japanese culture5. to get accustomed to business dialogues6. to prepare for study in Japan7. to prepare for a working holiday in Japan8. to prepare for employment in a Japanese company9. to prepare for employment in Japan 


